      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/21889418-the-signature-of-all-things">Quotes from The Signature of ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;I would like to spend the rest of my days in a place so silent–and working at a pace so slow–that I would be able to hear myself living.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
